ARCustomerDashboardWidgetCard is a CardView
    show labels
    left column is Logo.File
        display as portrait image
        missing image is random background
            foreground text is "<ShortName>"
    main column
        RepresentativeText
            no label
        EmailAddress
            no label
            link is "mailto:<Customer.EmailAddress>"
        PhoneNumber.TelephoneDisplay
            no label
            link is "tel:<Customer.PhoneNumber>"
